jade.gen
Class Traditional

java.lang.Object
  jade.gen.Traditional
All Implemented Interfaces:
Gen
public class Traditional
extends java.lang.Object
implements Gen

Uses binary space partitioning to make a map with rooms and corridors. By virtue of the partitioning tree, the maps are guaranteed to be connected. As a final step, some cycles are added to the tree to make the maps more interesting and playable.
